---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Book — DragonCraft" locale="en">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>The Narrative Engine</h1>
    <p>Content Operating System for the AI Era · Introduction + 22 Chapters</p>
  </div>

  <div class="book-cover-banner">
    <img src="/images/book-cover.jpg" alt="The Narrative Engine Cover" />
  </div>

  <div class="page-content">

    <section class="section">
      <div class="section-label">Methodology Foundation · Part 1</div>
      <div class="chapter-grid">

        <a class="chapter-card" href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T130519==z--引子__intro__book.org" target="_blank">
          <div class="chapter-num">Intro</div>
          <div class="chapter-body">
            <h3>Narrative Equality</h3>
            <p>Why stories are more persuasive than data — and why the AI era makes this more urgent than ever.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="chapter-card" href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T201739==z--叙事本能__chapter01__book.org" target="_blank">
          <div class="chapter-num">C01</div>
          <div class="chapter-body">
            <h3>Narrative Instinct</h3>
            <p>Why the human brain is naturally optimized for stories — the cognitive science behind narrative.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="chapter-card" href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T150421==z--叙事的本质__chapter02__book.org" target="_blank">
          <div class="chapter-num">C02</div>
          <div class="chapter-body">
            <h3>The Nature of Narrative</h3>
            <p>Plot, style, perspective, time, theme — five dimensions that determine how the same story unfolds.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="chapter-card" href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T150835==z--八刀解剖法__chapter03__book.org" target="_blank">
          <div class="chapter-num">C03</div>
          <div class="chapter-body">
            <h3>Eight-Cut Anatomy</h3>
            <p>A full-body CT scan of any narrative across 8 dimensions: history, dialectics, phenomenon, language, form, existence, aesthetics, meta-reflection.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="section-label">Scenario Skills · Part 2</div>
      <div class="chapter-grid">

        <a class="chapter-card" href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T152339==z--个人IP__chapter04__book.org" target="_blank">
          <div class="chapter-num">C04</div>
          <div class="chapter-body">
            <h3>Personal IP</h3>
            <p>Turning your experiences into narrative assets — the most worthwhile narrative practice ground.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="chapter-card" href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T152919==z--品牌叙事__chapter05__book.org" target="_blank">
          <div class="chapter-num">C05</div>
          <div class="chapter-body">
            <h3>Brand Narrative</h3>
            <p>Making users voluntarily认同 "who you are" — the narrative logic behind brand feeling.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="chapter-card" href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T153542==z--产品发布__chapter06__book.org" target="_blank">
          <div class="chapter-num">C06</div>
          <div class="chapter-body">
            <h3>Product Launch</h3>
            <p>Turning specs into surprises — the narrative rhythm where 3 seconds decide life or death at a launch event.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="chapter-card" href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T153825==z--创业融资__chapter07__book.org" target="_blank">
          <div class="chapter-num">C07</div>
          <div class="chapter-body">
            <h3>Startup Fundraising</h3>
            <p>Making investors believe "it's got to be you" — the narrative structure behind a great pitch deck.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="chapter-card" href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T190641==z--销售说服__chapter08__book.org" target="_blank">
          <div class="chapter-num">C08</div>
          <div class="chapter-body">
            <h3>Sales Persuasion</h3>
            <p>Letting customers persuade themselves — the core of sales narrative isn't the product, it's the problem.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="chapter-card" href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T191402==z--组织变革__chapter09__book.org" target="_blank">
          <div class="chapter-num">C09</div>
          <div class="chapter-body">
            <h3>Organizational Change</h3>
            <p>Turning strategy into shared belief — why most change initiatives fail due to narrative failure, not strategy.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="chapter-card" href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T193857==z--公益筹款__chapter10__book.org" target="_blank">
          <div class="chapter-num">C10</div>
          <div class="chapter-body">
            <h3>Charity Fundraising</h3>
            <p>Using one small story to drive big action — fundraising narrative in the age of compassion fatigue.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="chapter-card" href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T194441==z--社交媒体__chapter11__book.org" target="_blank">
          <div class="chapter-num">C11</div>
          <div class="chapter-body">
            <h3>Social Media</h3>
            <p>3-second hook + 45-second development + quotable close — narrative structure for the short-video era.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="chapter-card" href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T201918==z--教育开场__chapter12__book.org" target="_blank">
          <div class="chapter-num">C12</div>
          <div class="chapter-body">
            <h3>Education Opening</h3>
            <p>Pulling learners into state in 3 minutes — adult education openers that work aren't about "what" but "why you need to listen".</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="chapter-card" href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T201918==z--公关危机__chapter13__book.org" target="_blank">
          <div class="chapter-num">C13</div>
          <div class="chapter-body">
            <h3>PR Crisis</h3>
            <p>4A model turns "incident" into "story" — the narrative framework for the golden hour of crisis response.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="chapter-card" href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T201918==z--探索式叙事__chapter14__book.org" target="_blank">
          <div class="chapter-num">C14</div>
          <div class="chapter-body">
            <h3>Exploratory Narrative</h3>
            <p>Letting users discover Easter eggs themselves — people trust what they discover 3× more than what's told to them.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="section-label">AI-Era Narrative Tools · Part 3</div>
      <div class="chapter-grid">

        <a class="chapter-card" href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T162000==z--元Skill__chapter15__book.org" target="_blank">
          <div class="chapter-num">C15</div>
          <div class="chapter-body">
            <h3>MetaSkill</h3>
            <p>Turning narrative methods into AI-executable instructions — using prompts to let AI execute your narrative formulas.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="chapter-card" href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T162000==z--叙事记忆库__chapter16__book.org" target="_blank">
          <div class="chapter-num">C16</div>
          <div class="chapter-body">
            <h3>Narrative Memory Bank</h3>
            <p>Building your narrative assets — making every piece of content part of a continent, not an island.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="chapter-card" href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T162000==z--去AI化__chapter17__book.org" target="_blank">
          <div class="chapter-num">C17</div>
          <div class="chapter-body">
            <h3>De-AI-fication</h3>
            <p>Keeping "human flavor" in AI-assisted narratives — maintaining authenticity in the age of large language models.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="chapter-card" href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T162000==z--人机协作工作流__chapter18__book.org" target="_blank">
          <div class="chapter-num">C18</div>
          <div class="chapter-body">
            <h3>Human-AI Collaboration</h3>
            <p>A complete system from fragment to publish — how Xiao Chen cuts content work from 8 hours to 4 using AI.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="chapter-card" href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T162000==z--个人IP__chapter19__book.org" target="_blank">
          <div class="chapter-num">C19</div>
          <div class="chapter-body">
            <h3>Personal IP (Advanced)</h3>
            <p>Turning your resume into a story — the difference between "led digital transformation" and "improved decision efficiency by 40%".</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="chapter-card" href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T162000==z--开源项目叙事__chapter20__book.org" target="_blank">
          <div class="chapter-num">C20</div>
          <div class="chapter-body">
            <h3>Open Source Project Narrative</h3>
            <p>Letting code tell its own story — narrative strategy for GitHub project cold starts.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="chapter-card" href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T162000==z--叙事领导力__chapter22__book.org" target="_blank">
          <div class="chapter-num">C21</div>
          <div class="chapter-body">
            <h3>Narrative Evolution</h3>
            <p>We ourselves are the first test subjects — firsthand practice of the open-source writing model.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="chapter-card" href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/chapters/book/20260501T162000==z--叙事领导力__chapter22__book.org" target="_blank">
          <div class="chapter-num">C22</div>
          <div class="chapter-body">
            <h3>Narrative Leadership</h3>
            <p>From story to action — L1 corridor stories, L2 cultural narrative, L3 vision narrative, with Nadella and Musk case studies.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section github-cta">
      <p>Chapter source files hosted on GitHub with native .org rendering.<br/>
      <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/tree/main/chapters/book" target="_blank">View all chapters on GitHub →</a></p>
    </section>

  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .section { margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 16px;
    padding-bottom: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .chapter-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .chapter-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 16px;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 14px 18px;
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
  }

  .chapter-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .chapter-num {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    min-width: 36px;
    padding-top: 3px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .chapter-body {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .chapter-body h3 {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .chapter-body p {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .github-cta {
    background: rgba(192,57,43,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(192,57,43,0.12);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 16px 20px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .github-cta a { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500; }

  .book-cover-banner {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto 32px;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
  }

  .book-cover-banner img { width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }
</style>
